<p>Praise Break &amp; Jam is a platform for young artists who love to <i>priase</i> with their music, <i>break</i> it down to the people, and <i>jam</i> out with their audiences. All artist performing in this series have been asked to choose a local African American organization of their choice serving our communities and children.</p>
